- * ON HIGH

01:24.618 --> 01:26.587
*

01:26.620 --> 01:27.855
* TAKE ME HIGHER

01:27.888 --> 01:29.323
- HE'S AMAZING.

01:29.357 --> 01:31.325
- UNBELIEVABLE!

01:31.359 --> 01:34.795
- * TAKE ME HIGHER

01:34.828 --> 01:37.598
- WHEN DID HE MOVE TO TOWN?
- A COUPLE OF WEEKS AGO.

01:37.631 --> 01:39.533
- * TAKE ME HIGHER

01:39.567 --> 01:42.270
- I THINK HIS NAME'S BRANDON.

01:42.303 --> 01:45.539
- * COME ON

01:45.573 --> 01:48.409
- I HEAR HE'S GOT
