OUT OF HATE AND IGNORANCE.

46:56.948 --> 46:59.918
WE HAVE GOT TO STOP THEM.

46:59.951 --> 47:01.953
BUT IT'S NOT
GOING TO BE EASY.

47:01.987 --> 47:03.621
